<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَالفَرْدُ النِّسْبِيُّ:</span> إِنْ وَافَقَهُ غَيْرُهُ: فَهُوَ المُتَابِعُ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَإِنْ وُجِدَ مَتْنٌ يُشْبِهُهُ:</span> فَهُوَ الشَّاهِدُ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَتَتَبُّعُ الطُّرُقِ لِذَلِكَ:</span> هُوَ الِاعْتِبَارُ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>